# AcadPulse Frontend Dashboard

Build a professional, simple React+Vite dashboard for AcadPulse — an early warning system for at-risk students.

## Design Spec

- **Header**: "AcadPulse" on the left, notification bell + Login button on the right (login on extreme right, bell to its left)
- **Center Content**: 3 large tab cards stacked vertically — Attendance, Assignments, Marks — each with an icon
- **Color Palette**: Dark Blue `#1E3A8A`, Light Blue `#3B82F6`, Light Grey `#F3F4F6`, Red `#EF4444`
- **Layout**: Flexbox throughout
- **Style**: Professional, clean, simple — Google Fonts (Inter)

